## Corporate Identity (CI)

### Brand Colors (IMMER verwenden)

| Farbe | Hex | Tailwind-Klasse | Verwendung |
|-------|-----|-----------------|------------|
| **Primary** | `#00B3C7` | `brand-primary` | Primäre Aktionen, Links, Focus |
| Primary Hover | `#009AA8` | `brand-primary-hover` | Button-Hover-States |
| Primary Active | `#008494` | `brand-primary-active` | Button-Active-States |
| Primary Light | `#E5F8FA` | `brand-primary-light` | Badges, Highlights |
| **Dark** | `#333333` | `brand-dark` | Text, Icons, Borders |
| **Light** | `#E5F2F3` | `brand-light` | Sidebar-BG, Table-Hover |

### Semantic Colors

- **Success:** `#22C55E` (`ui-success`) - Erfolg, Aktiv, Online
- **Warning:** `#F59E0B` (`ui-warning`) - Warnung, Ausstehend
- **Error:** `#EF4444` (`ui-error`) - Fehler, Löschen, Offline
- **Info:** `#3B82F6` (`ui-info`) - Information, Hinweise

