## Grid-System & Spacing

### Standard-Layouts

```html
<!-- 50/50 -->
<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">...</div>

<!-- 33/33/33 -->
<div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4">...</div>

<!-- 66/33 (2:1) -->
<div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4">
  <div class="col-span-2">...</div>
  <div>...</div>
</div>

<!-- Responsive -->
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4">...</div>
```

### Spacing (konsistent verwenden)

- **Card/Panel Padding:** `p-4` (16px)
- **Grid Gap:** `gap-4` (16px)
- **Vertikale Abstände:** `space-y-4` (16px)
- **Section Margins:** `mb-6` (24px)

